{"tid":1888624,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"九巴獲日本城提供6.8萬口罩   網民：別忘了新巴城巴","createTime":"2020-02-20T10:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T07:56:49.000Z","uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a052cc69eb2e3dfe6ff46ce58455fa7e9139929","tid":1888624,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200220/_2020022014572968910.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200220%2F_2020022014572968910.jpg&h=7fac77e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200220/_2020022014573059811.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200220%2F_2020022014573059811.jpg&h=f04efae6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港汽車交通運輸業總工會九龍巴士分會主任黎兆聰表示，以每天上班的人數計算，相信約七萬個口罩數天便會耗盡，「唔係頂得幾耐」，但明白公司方面已四處尋找口罩供應，無奈全球口罩量緊絀。他又表示，早前曾因口罩短缺，有車長無口罩取用，個別車長惟有拒絕開工。<br />\n<br />\n四間巴士公司借用政府口罩 需全數歸還<br />\n九巴發言人昨（19日）證實，由於2月訂購的口罩未能如期付運，為員工提供的口罩數量緊絀，逐向政府尋求協助，九巴及龍運均獲借口罩，日後需要全數歸還；而新巴城巴亦曾向政府借用口罩，同樣需要歸還。"},{"pid":"220b006a2a1f844f87de64e0495de4e3fdbf63b4","tid":1888624,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:03:06.000Z","msg":"九巴新巴城巴龍運獲政府借CSI口罩 日後要全數歸還<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1887618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1887618</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t39.2147-6/p540x282/87229329_3215990435095172_2858758690670903296_n.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_ohc=m-oypuzI4T8AX-AgJJO&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=49cac2c3c9e1eae8a628151068a9abe5&amp;oe=5F00CA59\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft39.2147-6%2Fp540x282%2F87229329_3215990435095172_2858758690670903296_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_ohc%3Dm-oypuzI4T8AX-AgJJO%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3D49cac2c3c9e1eae8a628151068a9abe5%26oe%3D5F00CA59&h=4492f6a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e73935283bc5ed7fb4324da7da59c2185fd84e49","tid":1888624,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:03:28.000Z","msg":"九巴口罩不足，如同「吊緊鹽水」。他指，口罩放在站長室，一個月前供同事自由取用，有人一次拿數個甚至整盒，後來規定每人一日兩個，現時每日一個及需簽名領取，而且只提供予前線崗位，包括車長、站長、清潔工及督察，工程部及文職則不提供。此外，有員工反映，九巴提供的口罩部分太薄或太細，「好似小朋友口罩咁」。<br />\n<br />\n黎表示，17年前「沙士」時期，九巴協助員工家庭訂口罩，但是次新型冠狀病毒疫情卻愛莫能助，更曾徵詢工會可否呼籲員工捐出口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好讓九巴統籌分配予員工及家屬應急。他指，「同事都好擔心唔夠口罩用」，九巴及龍運合共約6,000名車長，每日營運需使用約7,000個口罩，冀政府可以協助服務業尋覓口罩貨源。"},{"pid":"2319e6f1bef9969c61f84db83f7c1d58f8b47765","tid":1888624,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:05:26.000Z","msg":"<em>David NG 九巴仔撲口罩... 撲到去日本🤣城<br />\nKMB 九巴專頁 日本城真係好好&lt;3 肯優先出售部份口罩比我哋 🥰<br />\n<br />\n黃盛輝 啲口罩駛唔駛全數歸還畀日本城？<br />\nKMB 九巴專頁 唔洗~ 因為日本城係出售比我哋🤣🤣<br />\n</em>"},{"pid":"4f060b0b3039a348bbd656291909601f6b545af3","tid":1888624,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"原來貴公司嘅司機因為冇口罩先至開唔到車，嗱，而家有口罩喇，冇藉口減班次啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkitalk.net/HKiTalk2/data/attachment/forum/202002/19/231353dm6oodvmy8omtcjt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkitalk.net%2FHKiTalk2%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F202002%2F19%2F231353dm6oodvmy8omtcjt.jpg&h=1b5510d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b05d48cb547d53c1eabee1565f5cd972edb90263","tid":1888624,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"樓主巴膠"},{"pid":"8d4c00f69daeebd58b18254e27a220ef782f9430","tid":1888624,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b05d48cb547d53c1eabee1565f5cd972edb90263","tid":1888624,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"樓主巴膠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/07/142713_9a2bf459beb7644ad47e6f1c830b8fa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F07%2F142713_9a2bf459beb7644ad47e6f1c830b8fa0.jpg&h=e6d9aaa4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b0cff0432f5afd579ef0ee42953ffd6223232ca","tid":1888624,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b05d48cb547d53c1eabee1565f5cd972edb90263","tid":1888624,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T10:15:00.000Z","msg":"樓主巴膠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:05:06.000Z","msg":"我搭開觀塘區"},{"pid":"04c0174c355c0bf46fd61d9e6b1154c3e3e0050b","tid":1888624,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"屌又係黎兆聰<br />\n硬係唔搵綠簿嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b2ccf6c648a8e4f778fad71d59acc9b08cbb32","tid":1888624,"uid":278906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VURvXjT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVURvXjT.png&h=977ad416&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72791a67ede47e116cb96012a7b119d91fc68b6c","tid":1888624,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04c0174c355c0bf46fd61d9e6b1154c3e3e0050b","tid":1888624,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"屌又係黎兆聰<br />\n硬係唔搵綠簿嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e2537426a4224eeae1602fc633b3f0c34bf763","tid":1888624,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04c0174c355c0bf46fd61d9e6b1154c3e3e0050b","tid":1888624,"uid":181474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"屌又係黎兆聰<br />\n硬係唔搵綠簿嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T07:56:49.000Z","msg":"巴士業職工會聯盟城巴理事長許漢傑指，城巴過年後不久已指口罩短缺，有一批原定2月中到貨，但最後脫期，他指明白公司為此向政府借口罩，若其他社福機構更有需要，政府應優先免費供應。他指公司早前曾容許每名司機每更可取兩個口罩，近期改為每更一個，他估計現用口罩是公司在外採購的批次，第一批是藍色較厚身ASTM（美國材料和試驗協會）Level 2級別，現時使用的第二批口罩是綠色較薄的ASTM Level 1級別。他指工會一早按《勞工法例》向公司表明，如沒有口罩保護不會開工，暫時無會員因缺口罩需要停工。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署回覆《蘋果》指，鑑於近期口罩供應緊張，專營巴士公司的口罩新訂單暫未到貨，經商討後，港府曾借用一定數量口罩給與巴士公司使用，讓他們維持正常服務。有關公司在收到新訂口罩後，需全數歸還政府。"}]}